0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-outline-level: 4; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Username and personal bio</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The user name must be a name that has meaning and not just symbols or numbers. It is prohibited to use any names that incite hatred, violence, or the use of any trademarks as a user name. It is not currently permitted to use company names as a user name, and the user is obligated to write his real name in his personal profile. Note that this name is not editable. <br>Personal photo: The user is obligated to put his real personal photo and not put a photo of another person in his account, or promotional photos... The personal biography must express the user, his skills, and his specialty in a brief manner. It is not allowed to add external means of communication or promotional phrases for other projects within the bio.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-outline-level: 4; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Commission is required</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The Malazoom platform commission is deducted from the person providing the service and not from the applicant. The person in charge does not have the right to ask the applicant to pay the Malazoom commission or indicate it. The applicant must submit his final offer directly after taking into account the Malazoom commission that will be deducted from the amount that Put it on display </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; background: white; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 0in 0in 0in 9.0pt;\"><span dir=\"LTR\" lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-outline-level: 4; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Refund of funds charged via Mazloum</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The balance is returned by opening a ticket at the Malzoom Help Center, and the return process is subject to several conditions, including </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">:</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Credits are available for return within a maximum of 14 days from the date of payment if the payment method provides a return option</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The amount will be returned after deducting the electronic payment fees from the amount, in addition to 14% of the fees for each return request.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The return will be made exclusively to the payment method that was used, as we carry out the </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Refund process </span><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">for the amounts to be recovered. <span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">Therefore, we ask you to confirm the method you intend to use before making the payment process, and then contact us through the Help Center if you wish to recover the balance </span></span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">.</span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-outline-level: 4; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Dealing with content</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Mulzoom website has the right, but is not obligated, to delete or hide offers or requests that violate the terms of the site or those that cause harm to the site or its users, without the user&rsquo;s notice.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -22.5pt; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -22.5pt; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Stop accounts</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The user uses a payment method that is stolen or not owned by him</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The account can be used by more than one person, whether they are a team or a company. Only one person is allowed to use the account in Mazloum and work on requests in it.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The user (the obligor) plays the role of an intermediary in requests, such that he receives a request as an obligor and then hires another person to work on it outside or within the obligatory platform (in this case, the intermediary will be suspended and obligated to pay any amounts due and carry out any work at the discretion of technical support)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The user attempts to defraud the employee by requesting full work in messages before hiring him</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The user causes any harm to any other user or any website</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The obligee evades paying the platform commission through external payment, and the ban is immediately final</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Insisting on communicating outside the Mulzum platform unnecessarily</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The obligated person does not follow up on the work after starting it without a fundamental reason, causing the applicant to waste his or her time</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The person obligated to publish a work not prepared by him in his exhibition of works</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Providing bids on projects that he does not master or performing low-quality work.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">The user impersonates another person on the site</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Uploading a personal photo to the account that is not a photo of the account owner himself, including using photos of public figures</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Selling the account. When the process of selling any account is discovered, it is immediately stopped along with its balance, and no party can benefit from it</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">You must create more than one account and use them for any reason</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Posting fake projects or spam</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Using </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Google AdWords </span><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">to advertise Al-Malzoom&rsquo;s business or any other content on the site</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.35pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">*** These terms are constantly updated</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: -22.5pt; line-height: normal; tab-stops: right .25in; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 0in 0in 0in 9.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><u><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(32, 33, 36); letter-spacing: 0.1pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">&nbsp;</span></span></u></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: -22.5pt; line-height: normal; tab-stops: right .25in; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 0in 0in 0in 9.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><u><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(32, 33, 36); letter-spacing: 0.1pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">&nbsp;</span></span></u></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; line-height: normal; tab-stops: right .25in; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 0in 0in 0in 9.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><u><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(32, 33, 36); letter-spacing: 0.1pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">&nbsp;</span></span></u></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" dir=\"RTL\" style=\"text-align: right; line-height: normal; tab-stops: right .25in; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 0in 0in 0in 9.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><u><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(32, 33, 36); letter-spacing: 0.1pt; background: white;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">&nbsp;</span></span></u></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; margin-right: 9.35pt; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><a name=\"_Toc157278583\"></a><a name=\"_Toc157278585\"></a><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">I. </span></strong><strong><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-EG\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">​Guarantee of rights</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Mulzoom website guarantees the rights of both parties if they adhere to the terms and if the agreement between them is completely clear from the beginning</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Your sharing of any private, banking, or other personal data with users is at your personal risk, and this does not relate to any payment operations you make on the platform, as that is 100% secure and is not a matter of sharing data.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 4; background: white; margin: 7.5pt 9.0pt 7.5pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">How does a person guarantee your rights?</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Malazoom website fully guarantees your financial rights, so there is no need for any worry. Be reassured when creating any new request or submitting your offers on the orders displayed on the site, as Malazoom website plays the role of mediator between the requester and the person requested and protects the financial rights of both parties in the event of compliance with the terms of the Malazoom website. The terms of the warranty and agreement are fully explained. <br>If you encounter any problems, do not hesitate to contact us and explain the problem and we will respond to you as soon as possible. Note that when resorting to technical support to resolve a problem, both parties must commit to accepting the ruling on it.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 4; background: white; margin: 7.5pt 9.0pt 7.5pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">So that we can always guarantee your rights, please make sure to follow the following rules</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 4; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Applicant</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Write your request in detail, explaining all the points required to be done very clearly in order to get the best offers suitable for your request. Also, specify a time period and an appropriate budget for the request.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">If the binding offer differs in duration and budget from the one you offered, and you choose it, the binding offer will be the one in effect in terms of implementation duration and budget.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">You can contact any supplier who adds an offer to your request, and the supplier can modify his offer after you contact him.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Any important information you give to the person in charge is at your personal risk: passwords, phone number, and personal accounts.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">You will not be able to modify any data related to your application after your application receives the first offer from applicants.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">When a problem arises with the person in charge, try to solve it amicably as long as he does not start or finish his work, as he has not received his money yet.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">After you accept the applicant\'s offer, you will be able to write to him within the application itself, without the need for any external means of communication.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">If the person on duty completes his work, he will request that the application be delivered and you will receive a notification about that. If you have any amendments or details that have not been completed in the application, you can ask the person on duty to complete them according to the rules of the profession.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">If you receive the order, this means that you got exactly what you wanted, and communication between you and the person obligated ended and he received his profits from the work, and you cannot cancel the order or request any amendment to it .</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">If the employee does not respond to you to complete the request within the specified period, you can cancel the work with him and evaluate him.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Do not ask the applicant for any points that are not stated in the application description, and remember to discuss all the details with him before you accept his offer and he begins work.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Electronic payment can be made using direct payment cards and credit cards when purchasing from merchants.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Payment fees will apply to electronic payment</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Do not use external transfers and do not request any means of communication, such as email, social accounts, or mobile phone...Malzoom website will not protect you if any communication takes place outside the website, and this matter may expose the account to closure.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 4; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">These terms are constantly updated.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 4; background: white; margin: 7.5pt 9.0pt 7.5pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Service provider</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Your offer must be clear in detail and related to the request for which you are submitting the offer, so study the matter carefully and provide a budget and time that is completely appropriate for you.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">You will not be able to modify your offer after adding it unless the applicant contacts you, then you can modify your offer.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Ask the applicant carefully about his application and its details before you begin it and explain to him what you will do, and do not request information that you do not need, such as phone numbers and passwords.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">After the applicant accepts your offer, the order amount will be reserved from his account balance on the Mulzoom website, and you will receive the amount when the request is received by its owner.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">You can communicate via Mazloum messages with the applicant at any time after he accepts your offer.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">After completing the order, you can click on the submit order button and a notification will be sent to the order holder.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">If your work is good and complete, the applicant will receive the application and you will receive the agreed upon amount.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Electronic payment can be made using direct payment cards and credit cards when purchasing from merchants.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Electronic payment payment fees will apply +14% of the fees value + fixed expenses.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Do not use external transfers and do not request any means of communication, such as email, social accounts, or mobile phone...Malzoom website will not protect you if any communication takes place outside the website, and this matter may expose the account to closure.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Placing or requesting external communication means in offers is prohibited and means losing the guarantee and protection of the Mazloum website directly, and may expose your account to closure at any time.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tab-stops: list .5in; background: white; margin: 0in 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">Submitting offers on projects that you are not proficient in working on and wasting your employers&rsquo; time through delay in implementation or non-implementation will lead to your account being evaluated negatively by them and may lead to the closure of your account on the Mulzoom website.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 4; background: white; margin: 7.5pt 9.0pt 0in 0in;\"><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black;\">*** These terms are constantly updated.</span></p>'),
